## 📊 Quick Reference

### Overview Table

| Concept | Pattern | Use Case |
|---------|---------|----------|
| **Server Component** | Default async component | Data fetching, DB access, SSR |
| **Client Component** | `'use client'` directive | Hooks, event handlers, interactivity |
| **Server Action** | `'use server'` directive | Mutations, form submissions |
| **Cache Component** | `'use cache'` + `cacheTag()` | Data caching with invalidation |
| **Route Handler** | `app/api/**/route.ts` | Webhooks, third-party integrations |
| **Dynamic Import** | `dynamic(() => import())` | Code splitting, heavy components |

### File Patterns

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `app/page.tsx` | Home page |
| `app/layout.tsx` | Root layout |
| `app/loading.tsx` | Loading state |
| `app/error.tsx` | Error boundary |
| `app/(group)/` | Route group (no URL) |
| `features/*/actions/*.ts` | Server actions |
| `features/*/queries/*.ts` | Data queries |

