## 💡 Key Insights

### Why Next.js 16 Matters

1. **React Server Components** → Réduit JS client de ~40%
2. **Cache Components** → Data fetching sans boilerplate
3. **Turbopack** → Build 10x plus rapide
4. **Partial Prerendering** → Best of SSR + SPA

### Optimisation Patterns

| Optimisation | Pattern | Bénéfice |
|--------------|---------|----------|
| Client JS | Server Components par défaut | -40% JS |
| Data fetching | Server Components/Actions | Performance serveur |
| Cache | `use cache` + tags | Invalidation fine-grained |
| Mutations | Server Actions | Moins de boilerplate |
| Images | next/image | Optimisation automatique |
| Build | Turbopack | 10x plus rapide |

